Create **Data/SeedData.cs** with a static method `SeedAsync(IServiceProvider services)` that:
- Creates roles: "Dispatcher", "Customer"
- Creates a dispatcher user: dispatcher@shipments.com / Dispatch1! (confirmed email, role "Dispatcher")
- Creates a customer user: customer@shipments.com / Customer1! (confirmed email, role "Customer")
